{"tid":166254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[國產導彈]北韓試射導彈失敗 「發射幾秒就爆炸」","createTime":"2017-03-22T03:43:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T00:55:47.000Z","uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"92ff02afa7c7fdad49ba42bcfdee4bf8c75df16c","tid":166254,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T03:43:07.000Z","msg":"南韓及美國軍方證實，北韓今早再有新一輪導彈試射，不過失敗告終。美國軍方發言人形容，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「有導彈在發射幾秒後就爆炸」</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n報道指導彈是在元山市（Wonsan）東部地區進行試射，但未知導彈的類型以及失敗的原因。今日適逢美韓年度軍演，初步估計北韓政府是想以試射示威。<br />\n<br />\n本月初北韓試射的4枚彈道導彈曾落入日本的西北部海域，惹來日本、美國及南韓強烈譴責。北韓較早前發布宣傳片，表明要炸毀美國的航母及轟炸機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又有人要處死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081792350b669ac5723fd9bb595cbe3e291fc780","tid":166254,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T03:48:14.000Z","msg":"前排美媒先吹奏北韓火箭技術提升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0631cc8e5025c0e97150349292cc6b8a3587ce","tid":166254,"uid":322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T03:52:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前排美媒先吹奏北韓火箭技術提升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>自爆速度提升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d013ce047f88cd4f4c72d173e6f92b31013766","tid":166254,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T03:52:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前排美媒先吹奏北韓火箭技術提升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌, 又屈唔到追加軍費喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"